snippet.title: Shantae and the Pirate's Curse Official Wii U Trailer
snippet.description:
When Sequin Land falls under a curse, Shantae must join forces with her arch nemesis Risky Boots to battle unimaginable evil! The third game in the Shantae series, exclusively on the Nintendo eShop for Wii U and 3DS.

Available 12.25.2014 on the North American Nintendo Wii U eShop!
